{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "beesuite-consolidated-2026",
        "name": "beeSuite Consolidated API",
        "description": "Consolidated Postman collection for all beeSuite services\n\n## Services Included:\n- eLeave Core (Port 3000) - Leave Management System\n- eLeave Tenant (Port 3001) - Multi-tenant Management\n- beeWhere (Port 3002) - Attendance & Workforce\n- eLeave Login (Port 3003) - Authentication Service\n- Beescheduler (Port 3004) - Scheduling System\n- eLeave WooCommerce (Port 3005) - WooCommerce Integration\n\n## Pre-request Scripts:\n- All authentication requests automatically encode passwords with base64\n- All protected endpoints check for valid access token\n- Token extraction from login responses\n\n## Post-response Scripts:\n- Login responses automatically extract and store access tokens\n- Token validation for protected endpoints\n\n## Environment Variables:\n- `base_url`: Default API base URL (use environment-specific URLs)\n- `access_token`: JWT token for authenticated requests\n- `eleave_core_url`: http://localhost:3000\n- `eleave_tenant_url`: http://localhost:3001\n- `beewhere_url`: http://localhost:3002\n- `eleave_login_url`: http://localhost:3003\n- `beescheduler_url`: http://localhost:3004\n- `eleave_woocommerce_url`: http://localhost:3005",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "base_url",
            "value": "http://localhost:3000",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "access_token",
            "value": "",
            "type": "string"
        }
    ],
    "event": [
        {
            "listen": "prerequest",
            "script": {
                "id": "consolidated-prerequest",
                "type": "text",
                "exec": [
                    "// Consolidated pre-request script",
                    "// Set base URL from environment if not already set",
                    "if (!pm.environment.get('base_url')) {",
                    "    pm.environment.set('base_url', 'http://localhost:3000');",
                    "}",
                    "// Encode password with base64 if present in request body",
                    "if (pm.request.body && pm.request.body.raw) {",
                    "    try {",
                    "        var body = JSON.parse(pm.request.body.raw);",
                    "        if (body.password && !body.password.startsWith('Y')) {",
                    "            body.password = btoa(body.password);",
                    "            pm.request.body.raw = JSON.stringify(body);",
                    "        }",
                    "    } catch (e) {",
                    "        // Body is not JSON or doesn't need processing",
                    "    }",
                    "}"
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
                "id": "consolidated-test",
                "type": "text",
                "exec": [
                    "// Consolidated test script",
                    "// Log response time for all requests",
                    "pm.test('Response time is reasonable', function () {",
                    "    pm.expect(pm.response.responseTime).to.be.below(10000);",
                    "});",
                    "// Check for successful response",
                    "pm.test('Response should be successful', function () {",
                    "    pm.expect(pm.response.successful).to.be.true;",
                    "});"
                ]
            }
        }
    ],
